表格维护信息的约束名称

CKT_REPAIRDEVICE


表格维护信息的服务器检验表达式

%RULES%


表格维护信息的选项

ON [PRIMARY]
END


表格维护信息的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('RepairDevice')
and type = 'U')
drop table RepairDevice
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: RepairDevice */
/*==============================================================*/
create table RepairDevice (
ID int identity(1,1),
RepairBillID varchar(20) not null,
RepareDate datetime not null,
DeviceType varchar(20) not null,
DeviceNo varchar(20) not null,
RepairType varchar(20) not null,
RepairContent varchar(200) not null,
BeginDate varchar(20) not null,
EndDate varchar(20) not null,
CompleteFlag bit not null,
Applier varchar(20) not null,
DutyMan varchar(20) not null,
Checker varchar(20) null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
MessageFlag bit null,
RepairHour numeric(18,2) null,
MaxMouldNum int null,
constraint PK_REPAIRDEVICE primary key (RepairBillID, DeviceNo)
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
